physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Round macules on the dorsal aspects of the hands and involvement of the nasal bridge.
physical_examinations.changes_over_time: Initially, the lesions improved partially but did not resolve, followed by new lesions on the face and crusting of the eyelids. After removal of the etonogestrel implant, substantial improvement was reported with minimal crusting and a decrease in size of lesions.
